item.title: Get Off Your Duff and GoVote.com
item.description:
You have a great new way to participate in the political life of America thanks to GoVote.com
With GoVote.com, you can Rate politicians, blogs, organizations, and more * Find all of your elected officials in one place * Find easy links to important web sites * Keep track of news that most important to you * Share your views on events, people, and organizations * More Take a few minutes to register and explore the site this weekend.
